Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.63,0:23:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由我來做
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.60,0:23:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做什麼阿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.50,0:23:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說做就要做
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.77,0:23:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以說做什麼阿
